data.description: REVISED PRICE. Single story, versatile use property on a sunny country lane. Large level parcel with serene, park-like yard. Could be 3/2 SFD, owner- user duplex, or 1031 trade target.  Currently 2/1 & 1/1.  Both units are vacant for buyer flexibility. Plenty of room to expand or add a unit via SB9. Located in unincorporated MV to make the process easier.  Amazing commute location. Just a few minutes to the local elementary school. At the doorstep of Muir Beach & the GGNRA.  Come see this exciting property with big upside.
